Full source at <a rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/sherifeid/3dobjects.git" >https://github.com/sherifeid/3dobjects.git</a>
PLEASE READ THE INSTRUCTIONS BEFORE CUSTOMIZING, FANS HAVE DIFFERENT DIMENSIONS AND ARE NOT STANDARD<br />
TO GET A CORRECT DESIGN YOU HAVE TO MAKE SURE THAT YOU ENTER THE CORRECT VALUES FOR 'Ls fan1' and 'Ls fan2' FOR EVERY FAN SIZE, THEY ARE DIFFERENT AND ARE NOT STANDARD<br />
If you find difficulty using the customizer just post a comment or send a message with both fan dimensions, the manifold angle and length and I will generate it  
This is my first attempt to design from scratch a programmable fan adapter that converts from ANY size to ANY other size with a few parameters. It also includes the ability to bend the airway (in a manifold tube shape) at any angle from 0 to 180 degrees. I posted the first size I need which is a 30mm to 80mm fan adapter with a 45 degree twist for my rostock max tri-head peek cooling. Comments are welcome, also attached the openscad source, please check the instructions tab for more details about how to customize it for you need.  
